  "texts": [
    "Participants reported a higher level of enjoyment when interacting with the chatbot than when completing the survey.",
    "They also perceived the chatbot's service quality to superior.",
    "Furthermore, the chatbot was deemed considerably easier to use, and satisfaction ratings were higher for the chatbot experience.",
    "Interestingly, the perceived usefulness and continuance intention were similar for both methods.",
    "In conclusion, these findings suggest that the chatbot provides a more engaging and satisfying user experience than traditional surveys, and may encourage increased digital public participation."
  ],
